7
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:20,060
Hot!

8
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,970
It's so hot!

9
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:23,860
You seem distracted today.

10
00:02:24,170 --> 00:02:25,120
That's true.

11
00:02:25,210 --> 00:02:26,800
Are you sick?

12
00:02:27,130 --> 00:02:30,150
We're almost done. You can go home first.

13
00:02:30,579 --> 00:02:32,670
