14
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:38,420
You can go to class, then.
I can take care of this.

15
00:02:39,950 --> 00:02:40,550
Here.

16
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,870
For you, if you want
to give it to someone.

17
00:02:43,329 --> 00:02:44,990
Thank you.

18
00:02:45,990 --> 00:02:46,940
Well...

19
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:49,030
I will go to my class.

20
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,450
