24
00:03:35,270 --> 00:03:37,370
Did you even think before you ask?

25
00:03:38,350 --> 00:03:39,810
The answer is very obvious.

26
00:03:40,450 --> 00:03:42,390
He's always late.

27
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:45,240
He's getting worse.

28
00:03:48,050 --> 00:03:49,850
Speak of the devil.

29
00:03:53,590 --> 00:03:54,900
It's for you.

30
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:57,050
For me?

31
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,150
Lucky me.

32
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:02,740
Let me see.

33
00:04:02,830 --> 00:04:04,130
What is it?

34
00:04:06,630 --> 00:04:08,150
Thai pudding with coconut topping!

35
00:04:08,230 --> 00:04:10,150
I love it. Let me eat it.

36
00:04:10,230 --> 00:04:10,960
We have to share this.

37
00:04:11,050 --> 00:04:12,010
No way.

38
00:04:12,540 --> 00:04:13,390
Give me three pieces.

39
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:14,310
No!

40
00:04:14,710 --> 00:04:15,780
