41
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:16,709
No. He gave it to us.

42
00:04:16,790 --> 00:04:17,630
Manaow!

43
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,620
Why does he seem so weird today?

44
00:04:23,610 --> 00:04:25,670
He is acting weird.

45
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:28,550
Did he put something weird
in the dessert too?

46
00:04:32,050 --> 00:04:35,090
What's wrong? What is your symptom?
Tell me.

47
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:35,870
What?

48
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,550
Are you sure?

49
00:04:38,110 --> 00:04:39,170
It's nothing.

50
00:04:39,250 --> 00:04:41,250
Nothing at all...

51
00:04:41,409 --> 00:04:42,930
