I haven't seen him in ten years.

53
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,770
I'm nervous.

54
00:04:50,130 --> 00:04:51,680
That's why.

55
00:04:51,770 --> 00:04:53,330
He's overthinking.

56
00:04:53,850 --> 00:04:57,090
