57
00:04:57,170 --> 00:04:58,780
Let's find something to eat.

58
00:04:58,860 --> 00:05:00,630
Fatty!

59
00:05:04,130 --> 00:05:05,250
By the way,

60
00:05:05,330 --> 00:05:08,570
I saw a new restaurant yesterday.

61
00:05:08,650 --> 00:05:09,490
Do you guys want to go?

62
00:05:09,570 --> 00:05:10,510
