63
00:05:10,590 --> 00:05:11,490
Right in front of our campus.

64
00:05:11,570 --> 00:05:12,850
You just called me fatty.

65
00:05:12,930 --> 00:05:13,900
Manaow, you're not fat.

66
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:15,430
Don't listen to Team.

67
00:05:15,850 --> 00:05:17,850
You guys are such liars.

68
00:05:18,170 --> 00:05:20,950
I don't think we can go today.

69
00:05:21,030 --> 00:05:22,210
Why not?

70
00:05:22,290 --> 00:05:23,590
Look.

71
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:26,540
Hello, Dean.

72
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:27,470
Hi.

73
00:05:28,090 --> 00:05:29,810
You're here to see Pharm?

74
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:32,290
I have a date with him.

75
00:05:32,990 --> 00:05:34,030
That's why.

76
00:05:34,110 --> 00:05:35,960
