and you didn't tell me.

77
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:38,470
You know, Pharm couldn't
concentrate in class.

78
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:40,550
He acted like this.

79
00:05:41,290 --> 00:05:43,300
I didn't know what was wrong with him.

80
00:05:44,490 --> 00:05:46,700
He didn't answer me
when I asked him questions.

81
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:48,790
I think he was overthinking
about something.

82
00:05:51,150 --> 00:05:52,890
Why? What's wrong?

83
00:05:55,130 --> 00:05:56,350
Nothing.

84
00:05:57,150 --> 00:05:58,670
Are you sure?

85
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:04,450
Well...

86
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,550
Let's eat together later, then.

87
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,090
Okay.

88
00:06:08,910 --> 00:06:10,390
By the way,

89
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:11,230
next week,

90
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:12,740
the short film that I was in,

91
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:14,830
the result will be announced soon.

92
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:17,850
Everyone was complimenting our Chor Muang.

93
00:06:17,930 --> 00:06:18,860
Thank you.

94
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:21,980
Keep our fingers crossed.
Let's celebrate if I win.

95
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:23,330
You can come with us, too.

96
00:06:23,410 --> 00:06:24,810
You're paying, right?

97
00:06:24,890 --> 00:06:25,430
Of course!

98
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:27,000
Are you sure?

99
00:06:27,090 --> 00:06:29,090
Let's think about this after I win.

100
00:06:29,450 --> 00:06:30,850
But right now...

101
00:06:32,110 --> 00:06:33,850
We have to go.

102
00:06:34,110 --> 00:06:35,670
See you guys later.

103
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:37,310
Goodbye.

104
00:06:37,550 --> 00:06:39,290
I'm off.

105
00:06:40,710 --> 00:06:41,980
Bye-bye.

106
00:06:46,850 --> 00:06:48,730
Let's go.

107
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:51,290
I want to eat something that you cook.

108
00:06:52,190 --> 00:06:53,030
Okay.

109
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:57,850
Pineapple fried rice.

110
00:06:57,930 --> 00:07:00,560
Let's put lots of Chinese sausage
and pork floss.

111
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,230
That's enough.

112
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:12,930
Let's pay.

113
00:07:13,010 --> 00:07:15,010
We won't be able to finish all the food.

114
00:07:21,470 --> 00:07:23,550
I want a bigger fridge.

115
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:27,390
You're so small. Why do you need
a bigger fridge?

116
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:31,910
I can make more desserts for you to eat.

117
00:07:33,710 --> 00:07:36,120
We can buy a bigger one
when we move into a house.

118
00:07:36,210 --> 00:07:37,890
I think a condo is too small.

119
00:07:38,770 --> 00:07:40,110
Which house?

120
