The house that we will live in together.

121
00:07:45,810 --> 00:07:48,030
I prefer to live in a house
rather than a condo.

122
00:07:56,690 --> 00:07:58,580
I will throw this away first.

123
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:19,010
You won't let me pay for anything.

124
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:23,610
Most of the things we bought

125
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:26,610
are for me and my club members.

126
00:08:27,970 --> 00:08:29,920
But I use them too.

127
00:08:30,010 --> 00:08:31,230
Am I right?

128
00:08:31,730 --> 00:08:34,210
It's my repayment for your water
and electricity bills.

129
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:36,830
Also, for the time you spent
being my chef.

130
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:40,860
You're such a strict businessman.

131
00:08:41,210 --> 00:08:42,330
I am.

132
00:08:43,070 --> 00:08:44,970
Because my boyfriend studies economics.

133
00:08:45,050 --> 00:08:46,870
That's why I have to be strict.

134
00:08:47,090 --> 00:08:49,670
Or else he might ditch me.

135
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:52,690
