201
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:00,340
That's good.

202
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,230
I can see you clearly.

203
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:05,110
That's not good at all.

204
00:15:09,210 --> 00:15:10,530
It is.

205
00:15:10,830 --> 00:15:12,490
Dean.

206
00:15:17,090 --> 00:15:18,610
Dean.

207
00:15:18,890 --> 00:15:20,270
Dean.

208
00:15:22,690 --> 00:15:24,030
Stop it.

209
00:15:24,110 --> 00:15:26,110
I surrender.

210
00:15:34,010 --> 00:15:35,710
I love you.

211
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:41,230
I love you too.

212
00:16:45,450 --> 00:16:46,650
