for half an hour.

215
00:16:54,290 --> 00:16:55,990
Is he dead now?

216
00:16:56,170 --> 00:16:57,990
Why didn't he go back home?

217
00:16:58,690 --> 00:17:00,630
He told me he's fine.

218
00:17:05,550 --> 00:17:07,690
Are you going to see him?

219
00:17:11,790 --> 00:17:12,770
Yes.

220
00:17:13,089 --> 00:17:15,609
Can you pass some medicine to him?

221
00:17:19,260 --> 00:17:20,470
And some water too.

222
00:17:22,450 --> 00:17:23,990
I'll be right back.

223
00:17:48,870 --> 00:17:49,710
In.

224
00:17:58,810 --> 00:18:00,330
Take this medicine.

225
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:01,890
Thank you.

226
00:18:11,390 --> 00:18:13,230
I hope that you will always be happy.

227
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:54,610
Do you like my hands?

228
00:18:57,570 --> 00:18:58,550
I do.

229
00:18:59,490 --> 00:19:01,590
They remind me of my dad's hands.

230
00:19:05,570 --> 00:19:07,210
I'm just kidding.

231
00:19:07,290 --> 00:19:09,290
You're not my daddy.

232
00:19:13,090 --> 00:19:14,020
Look.

233
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:16,110
Your hands are bigger than my face.

234
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:21,350
Stop being so cute.

235
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:23,270
Or you might not be able to get up.

236
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:25,350
Dean.

237
00:19:25,690 --> 00:19:27,390
Stop it.

238
00:19:27,670 --> 00:19:28,490
Stop it now.

239
00:19:28,570 --> 00:19:29,000
I won't.

240
00:19:29,090 --> 00:19:30,750
Dean.

241
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:31,870
Stop.

242
00:19:31,950 --> 00:19:32,920
You smell nice.

243
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,250
Dean.

244
00:19:35,250 --> 00:19:36,930
Stop teasing me.

245
00:19:42,410 --> 00:19:43,320
Are you hungry?

246
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:47,550
I'm hungry.

247
00:19:47,630 --> 00:19:48,850
Hungry for food?

248
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:50,860
Food, of course.

249
00:19:50,950 --> 00:19:52,350
Dean...

250
00:19:54,870 --> 00:19:57,160
I will buy some porridge for you, then.

251
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,650
Okay.

252
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:03,590
Should I go?

253
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:05,030
Just go.

254
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:07,110
I'm hungry.

255
00:20:07,210 --> 00:20:09,110
