256
00:20:13,570 --> 00:20:15,210
Fine. I'll go.

257
00:20:16,030 --> 00:20:16,790
I'll be right back.

258
00:20:16,870 --> 00:20:18,230
Okay.

259
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:26,420
